 Twitch 因人工智能问题取消裸体艺术新规定https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/twitch-rolls-back-new-nude-art-rules-over-ai-concerns-3560354?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=twitch-rolls-back-新裸体艺术规则对人工智能的关注Ali ShutlerMon, 18 Dec 2023 12:04:52 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsAIVideo Game Culture https://www.nme.com/?p=3560354 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Twitch-Credit-Ink-Drop-Alamy-Stock-Photo.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="抽搐" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Twitch-Credit-Ink-Drop-Alamy-Stock-Photo.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Twitch-Credit-Ink-Drop-Alamy-Stock-Photo-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Twitch-Credit-Ink-Drop-Alamy-Stock-Photo-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Twitch-Credit-Ink-Drop-Alamy-Stock-Photo-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Twitch-Credit-Ink-Drop-Alamy-Stock-Photo-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Twitch-Credit-Ink-Drop-Alamy-Stock-Photo-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我们走得太远了”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/twitch-rolls-back-new-nude-art-rules-over-ai-concerns-3560354">Twitch 因人工智能担忧而取消裸体艺术新规定的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Twitch-Credit-Ink-Drop-Alamy-Stock-Photo.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="抽搐" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Twitch-Credit-Ink-Drop-Alamy-Stock-Photo.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Twitch-Credit-Ink-Drop-Alamy-Stock-Photo-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Twitch-Credit-Ink-Drop-Alamy-Stock-Photo-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Twitch-Credit-Ink-Drop-Alamy-Stock-Photo-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Twitch-Credit-Ink-Drop-Alamy-Stock-Photo-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Twitch-Credit-Ink-Drop-Alamy-Stock-Photo-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>由于对<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/ai">人工智能</a>的担忧， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/twitch">Twitch</a>被迫改变流媒体平台上裸体艺术的新的、宽松的指导方针。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/how-ai-is-pushing-the-boundaries-of-entertainment-3409263">超越人类想象：人工智能如何突破娱乐界限</a></strong></li></ul><p>上周，Twitch 对性内容和裸露的指导方针进行了几处修改，禁止了一些使用摄像机角度使其看起来像是赤裸上身的主播 [来自<a href="https://www.pcgamer.com/twitch-relaxes-about-nudity-after-viral-topless-streams-says-you-can-be-sexy-on-stream-so-long-as-its-artistic-or-fictionalized/">PC Gamer</a> ]。</p><p>新规则包括对乳房和生殖器的“绘画、动画或雕刻”描绘采取更宽松的立场，并允许“对裸体的艺术描绘”。</p><p> “这次更新的一部分包括改变我们对待虚构裸体的方式，”Twitch 在<a href="https://safety.twitch.tv/s/article/Sexual-Content-Policy-Update?language=en_US">博客</a>中写道。 “多年来，我们从艺术家那里听到我们的内容政策受到限制。在进行此更新时，我们试图响应这些请求，并允许 Twitch 上蓬勃发展的艺术家社区在他们的艺术中利用人类形态。”</p><p>然而，就在新规则生效两天后，Twitch<a href="https://x.com/Twitch/status/1735677597831356789" target="_blank" rel="noopener">确认</a>将取消部分更改。 </p><figure id="attachment_3453188" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3453188" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3453188" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/twitch-streamers-protest-branded-content-policy.jpg" alt="Twitch 主播反对该公司新的品牌内容政策，现在该政策已被撤回。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/twitch-streamers-protest-branded-content-policy.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/twitch-streamers-protest-branded-content-policy-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/twitch-streamers-protest-branded-content-policy-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/twitch-streamers-protest-branded-content-policy-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/twitch-streamers-protest-branded-content-policy-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/twitch-streamers-protest-branded-content-policy-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3453188" class="wp-caption-text">人们玩电子游戏。图片来源：Ron Lach，来自 Pexels</figcaption></figure><p> Twitch 表示：“经过反思，我们认为这一改变太过分了。” “裸体的数字描绘提出了一个独特的挑战——人工智能可以用来创建逼真的图像，而且很难区分数字艺术和摄影。”</p><p> “因此，从今天起，我们将取消艺术裸体的变化。展望未来，无论采用何种媒体，Twitch 上都将不允许出现真实或虚构的裸体描述。”该平台在为更新造成的混乱致歉之前确认道。</p><p>去年 12 月，数百名艺术家<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/artists-protest-use-of-ai-generated-artwork-on-portfolio-site-artstation-3366778">在专业作品集网站 Artstation 上抗议使用人工智能创作的艺术作品</a>。</p><p>在其他消息中，Larian 首席执行官 Swen Vincke 表示， <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/baldurs-gate-iii">《博德之门 3》</a></em>永远不会在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-game-pass">Xbox Game Pass</a>上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-will-never-come-to-xbox-game-pass-3560347">发布</a>。 “我们制作了一款大型游戏，所以我认为为此付出的代价是合理的。这让我们能够继续制作其他游戏。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/twitch-rolls-back-new-nude-art-rules-over-ai-concerns-3560354">Twitch 因人工智能担忧而取消裸体艺术新规定的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
